# CODEOWNERS file

# Defines the code ownership rules. Specified users/groups will be automatically requested for review

# when changes are made to specific files or directories.

# Example: Assign ownership of the docs directory
docs/ @doc-maintainer

# Example: Assign multiple owners to the src directory
src/ @frontend-dev @backend-dev

# Example: Single file ownership for Docker-related files
Dockerfile @devops-lead

# Catch-all rule (default owners for any changes)
* @project-maintainer
